<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Inventory Management Solution</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: whitesmoke;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .flex-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .hero{
            width:1000px;
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: antiquewhite;
        }

        .cta {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: antiquewhite;
        }

        .hero-content, .cta-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .hero img, .cta img {
            width: 45%;
            max-width: 500px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .hero-text, .cta-text {
            width: 50%;
        }

            .hero-text h1, .cta-text h2 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                color: #333;
            }

            .hero-text p, .cta-text p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                color: #666;
            }

            .hero-text .signup, .cta-text .signup {
                margin-top: 20px;
                padding: 15px 30px;
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

        .features {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .features h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
                color: #333;
            }

        .features-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            width: 30%;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .feature-item h3 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
                color: #333;
            }

            .feature-item p {
                font-size: 1em;
                color: #666;
            }

        .cta-text {
            text-align: left;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            footer .footer-content {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-around;
            }

                footer .footer-content nav a {
                    color: #fff;
                    margin: 0 15px;
                    text-decoration: none;
                }

            footer .footer-contact p {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

            footer .footer-logo img {
                height: 40px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>


    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content flex-container">
                <img src="~/assets/warehouse.png" alt="warehouse" class="hero-image" />
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <h1>Your Ultimate Inventory Management Solution</h1>
                    <p>Simplify and optimize your stock management with Inventory, the ultimate inventory solution.</p>
                    <button class="signup">Sign-up</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Unlock Powerful Capabilities</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Reporting and Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Generate detailed reports on stock valuation, sales performance, and more, providing valuable insights for strategic planning.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Real-time Updates</h3>
                    <p>Get immediate access to accurate stock movement information, ensuring a real-time and dynamic view of your inventory status.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Customizable Dashboards</h3>
                    <p>Arrange widgets according to your preferences, providing a personalized and focused view of crucial metrics for your business.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content flex-container">
                <img src="~/assets/inventory.png" alt="inventory" class="cta-image" />
                <div class="cta-text">
                    <h2>Experience the ultimate in speed and precision for your inventory needs.</h2>
                    <p>Say goodbye to manual data entry and hello to unparalleled speed and accuracy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

